com.software.reuze

Class ff_3DSModel.MaterialInfo3DS

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.software.reuze.ff_3DSModel.MaterialInfo3DS
  • Enclosing class:
    ff_3DSModel

    public static class ff_3DSModel.MaterialInfo3DS
extends Object
    This holds the information for a material. It may be a texture map of a color. Some of these are not used, but I left them because you will want to eventually read in the UV tile ratio and the UV tile offset for some models.
